</h1>","          ","          </div>","          <div class=\"col-sm-6 text-right\">","            <ul class=\"breadcrumb pull-right\">","                <li><a href=\"../\">Home</a></li>","                <li><a href=\"../technologies/\">Technologies</a></li>","                <li class=\"active\">Microsoft Technology</li>","            </ul>","          </div>","          ","          </div>","          </div>","          <br>","        </div>","        </section>","<section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">    ","<div class=\"row\">","    <div class=\"col-sm-9\"><br>","      ","\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"methodText\"><strong>Microsoft’s cloud solution, Azure</strong> is enabling organizations of all sizes to get to the cloud quicker with maximum affordability and flexibility. The Azure platform is used to deliver superior performance while helping to control costs. Microsoft Azure can extend your infrastructure and provides scalable, durable cloud storage, backup and recovery solutions for any data, big and small.</p>","\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"methodText\"><strong>Miracle</strong> delivers innovative <strong>public, private and hybrid</strong> cloud integration services with deep technical expertise that supports you and your solution. Our team will help assess your needs and recommend the best cloud strategy for your needs.</p>","\t\t\t\t\t\t\t","\t\t\t\t\t","\t<!--<div class=\"row\">","\t\t    <div class=\"col-sm-5\">","\t\t        <img src=\"img/career.png\" class=\"img-responsive\" width=\"400px\">","\t\t    </div>","\t\t     <div class=\"col-sm-7\">","\t\t         \t<p class=\"methodText\">We are one of the few companies that has perfected the hybrid On-demand Models specializing on these Niche skills, and are backed by state-of-the-art facilities at multiple locations around the globe. Based on the Microsoft technologies, we are implementing, designing, and integrating solutions across a variety of industries and practice areas.We are one of the few companies th